NudgePay Extension

Load this folder as an unpacked extension (Chrome > Extensions > Developer mode).

Setup steps
1) Update the website extension id in website/app.js.
2) If you change the website URL, update externally_connectable in manifest.json.
3) Click "Send to Extension" in the dashboard to store the schema in chrome.storage.local.

Popup UI
- Open the extension popup while on Amazon or Uber Eats checkout pages.
- The popup reads the detected order total and compares it to the stored budget.
